Package com.cy_siao.model.person

Class Person

java.lang.Object
com.cy_siao.model.person.Person
public class Person extends Object
Represents a person with various personal attributes such as ID, name, gender, age, place of birth, social security number, and an associated address. This class manages personal information and restrictions for individuals in the system.
